{"tid":810132,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[食鬼食評]—清真牛肉餡餅","createTime":"2018-09-07T16:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T03:24:04.000Z","uid":182683,"like":9,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c27a60900080fd21e6bcc48b13c9badca427d6e2","tid":810132,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T16:45:57.000Z","msg":"地點：清真牛肉館<br />\n<br />\n今日咁岩去樂富搵人，專登入黎依間好出名嘅清真餐廳，門口勁多明星相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n聽講合乎教條嘅野食好似好麻煩，殺嘅過程仲好殘忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，不過我唔係道德撚，盡量食少啲！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/08/003841_685d632ebe37edfedc37f6ae897a64af.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F08%2F003841_685d632ebe37edfedc37f6ae897a64af.png&h=9485a93f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n牛肉餡餅2件$38<br />\n⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n味道：<br />\n首先個表皮都煎得幾脆同好薄，一啖咬落去即刻爆汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，真係超多唔係講笑，應該都係好似小籠包咁整嫁啦。<br />\n至於個餡食到啲蔥,芹菜,蒜,胡椒仲有啲唔識嘅香料，其實好似生煎包啲味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，只不過用左牛肉啲味濃啲同埋豉油味有啲重，自己覺得咸左少少。<br />\n⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n價錢：<br />\n$38咁大件都算抵食，而且餡都幾多。<br />\n⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n其實本人係唔鍾意食皮薄餡多嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，有啲野食可以(小籠包,春卷...)，但有<br />\n好似依類餡餅/包類嘅野食其實要食到個麵包嘅味先會平衡番個餡，所以個包/皮其實都要整得好味同埋唔好咁多餡，下下餡多不如剩係買啲餡食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n不過我問身邊嘅人都好似普遍鍾意餡多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，其實係我奇怪定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？！<br />\n⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n評分：6/10<br />\n評語：唔係好岩我🤪<br />\n<br />\nIg:<a href=\"https://instagram.com/hkfoodghost\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fhkfoodghost&d=jscOkhO2TpumRN1fB%2Fr55DOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=e8cc99fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/hkfoodghost</a><br />\n我ig有食個段片，懶得up youtube<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nYoutube(整野食):<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCqRF5PLGsAWPGjluK1DoBNw/featured\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCqRF5PLGsAWPGjluK1DoBNw%2Ffeatured&d=jscOkhO2TpumRN1fB%2Fr55DOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=5e96bc19\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCqRF5PLGsAWPGjluK1DoBNw/featured</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a3189f88091e79072b6044ea93b2d5cc1cd00bd","tid":810132,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T16:55:09.000Z","msg":"馬家莊清真館好食好多"},{"pid":"e3359218a7373df66d98e069a2121368d756e8e5","tid":810132,"uid":22007,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T16:59:54.000Z","msg":"&quot;包類嘅野食其實要食到個麵包嘅味先會平衡番個餡&quot; <br />\n<br />\n極度同意呢句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n有時真係唔明點解有D人食麵包淨係食D餡唔食外邊層麵包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90d7a9c690c88746f34d33b7eb9b2d142610e8cc","tid":810132,"uid":144312,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T17:08:05.000Z","msg":"呢間野最好食係咖哩羊腩飯，你走寶"},{"pid":"45185db6cb5b7a968081cee602a6b88e9a55cc3a","tid":810132,"uid":7206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T17:13:11.000Z","msg":"清真食品不嬲高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"